Class Toolset

  • java.lang.Object
    • se450.elevator.common.Toolset

  • public class Toolset
extends java.lang.Object
    Toolset shared for all project to get current delta time and do formated print.

    • Field Detail

      • DEBUG

        public static boolean DEBUG
        Boolean flag for current running mode. true - Running on debug mode. false - Running on normal mode. Common.print("debug", String message) won't print anything at this mode.

    • Method Detail

      • init

        public static void init()
        Toolset is a Singleton class. This method will create the only Toolset instance. It is a multi-thread safe implementation. Make sure this method be invoked during program start so it knows the program start time.
